Package de.fhg.fit.biomos.sensorplatform.control

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SampleCollector
    A SampleCollector decides, what to do further with a new calculated Sample.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CC2650SampleCollector
    CC2650SampleCollector stores different types of CC2650 Samples to the database.
    Controller
    This class defines the general control flow of the sensorplatform.
    HeartRateSampleCollector
    HeartRateSampleCollector stores heart rate samples to the database and it is able to upload those samples to an external webinterface.
    PulseOximeterSampleCollector
    PulseOximeterSampleCollector stores pulse oximeter samples to the database.
    SensorOverseer
    A new instance of SensorOverseer is used for every recording period.
    SensorWrapperFactory
    Factory for creating sensor objects.
